= JQuery Narrative Select Plugin

http://github.com/gdakram/
  
= DESCRIPTION & DEMO

http://gdakram.github.com/jquery-narrative-select

= INTRODUCTION

A JQuery tooltip plugin to make your drop-down list look and perform uniformly cross-platform. 

= USAGE

<!-- CSS -->
<style type="text/css">
  @import url("/path/to/jquery.narrativeselect/jquery.narrativeselect.css");
</style>    
<!-- JS -->        
<script type="text/javascript" src="/path/to/jquery.latest.js"></script> 
<script type="text/javascript" src="/path/to/jquery.narrativeselect.js"></script> 
<script type="text/javascript">
//--<![CDATA[
  $("select").narrativeselect();
//--]]>
</script>